---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/tailwind.css";
---

<Layout title="About | Hitesh Joshi" description="Learn more about Hitesh Joshi, founder and technology enthusiast.">
    <Header />

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-dark max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                About Me
            </h1>

            <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    Hey there! I'm Hitesh Joshi, a founder and technology enthusiast passionate about building
                    things that matter. Currently, I'm the CEO of Ploton Labs, Inc., where we're working on
                    exciting projects at the intersection of technology and human experience.
                </p>

                <p>
                    My journey in tech has been a fascinating ride through various domains - from deep diving
                    into system architecture to exploring the latest in AI and machine learning. I believe in
                    the power of technology to solve real-world problems and create meaningful impact.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                    What I Do
                </h2>

                <p>
                    I wear many hats, but at the core, I'm a builder. Whether it's architecting scalable
                    systems, leading product development, or mentoring the next generation of developers,
                    I'm always excited about creating something new.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                    Why This Blog?
                </h2>

                <p>
                    This blog is my digital garden - a place where I share thoughts, learnings, and
                    experiences from my journey. Topics range from technical deep-dives and startup
                    insights to philosophical musings about technology's role in our lives.
                </p>

                <p>
                    I believe in learning in public and sharing knowledge openly. Every post here is
                    either something I've learned, something I'm exploring, or something I think might
                    help others on their journey.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
                    Let's Connect
                </h2>

                <p>
                    I'm always excited to connect with fellow builders, thinkers, and curious minds.
                    Feel free to reach out:
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mt-6">
                    <a
                        href="https://twitter.com/hiteshjoshi"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M23.953 4.57a10 10 0 01-2.825.775 4.958 4.958 0 002.163-2.723c-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184a4.92 4.92 0 00-8.384 4.482C7.69 8.095 4.067 6.13 1.64 3.162a4.822 4.822 0 00-.666 2.475c0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096a4.904 4.904 0 01-2.228-.616v.06a4.923 4.923 0 003.946 4.827 4.996 4.996 0 01-2.212.085 4.936 4.936 0 004.604 3.417 9.867 9.867 0 01-6.102 2.105c-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067a13.995 13.995 0 007.557 2.209c9.053 0 13.998-7.496 13.998-13.985 0-.21 0-.42-.015-.63A9.935 9.935 0 0024 4.59z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Follow me on Twitter
                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="https://bento.me/joshi"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"></path>
                        </svg>
                        View all my links
                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="https://cal.com/ploton"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-gray-100 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Schedule a call
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
                    <Footer />
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </main>
</Layout>
